Magazine template
=================

The _Magazine_ template is designed to handle a diversity of published material: short posts, long essays, images, links all flow together. The index page features your most recently published posts in full. {{#featured.length}}These people use the _Magazine_ template:{{/featured.length}}

Customize this template
-----------------------

You can adjust the colors and fonts of the _Magazine_ template using Blot's template editor: there's no coding required.

The source code of the _Magazine_ template is dedicated to the public domain, so you can make and distribute modifications to it as you please.

[View the source code](https://github.com/davidmerfield/Blot/tree/master/app/templates/latest/magazine)

About the folder
----------------

The [preview]({{{preview}}}) for the _Blog_ template contains interviews from Wikinews. You can get a full copy of the source folder used to generate this site.

